# Build context is the repo root. Keep it lean: deps are installed inside the
# image, build artifacts and local state must not leak in.
**/node_modules
**/build
**/.svelte-kit
**/coverage
**/test-results
**/playwright-report

# Local SQLite databases (dev/e2e) — never bake these into the image
**/*.db
**/*.db-shm
**/*.db-wal
**/*.db-journal

# Secrets and local env, but keep the examples for reference
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example
!**/.env.local.example

.git
.github
.vscode
**/*.log
